                        "text": "A creature struck by Two Tusk's slime squirt becomes clumsy 1 and takes a \u20135-foot penalty to Speed for 1 hour or until the slime is removed. A PC can use an Interact action to splash swamp water on themself to wash away the stuff and remove this penalty."
